---{ Gameplay }---
☐ Very good
☑ Good
☐ It's just gameplay
☐ Mehh
☐ Watch paint dry instead
☐ Just don't

Introducing a fun and just superbly implemented way to traverse over obstacles certain fences, is the "bat mode". As a vampire, turning into a bat and beiong able to fly across rocks, fallen trees, fences, and avoiding the speed reduction from walking through high grass, it's clear that the developers are fully invested in the game's theme. This also shows that instead of only slapping a vampire aesthetic over a farming sim, they are building a rich story that cares about details of how life as a farmer would actually be if your bed is a beautifully crafted mahogany coffin and your ever following you pet is a black cat with three eyes that demands attention and petting.

