Game is very fun, the visuals are quite appealing, and it just gives a very good sense of belonging even though its unlikely we can relate to being vampires. For now. 8/10.

---{ Nice-to-have Features }---
After playing for a bit, these are some features I would love for them to find their way into the final release.

☐ Organize button for items in inventory and storage locations
☐ A quick press of a button to remove the tool currently being held 
☐ Gates. I'd prefer to create enclosed areas for different animals, but the use of certain fences doesn't allow for any way to cross over them, even in "bat" mode. Some of these fences are just too pretty to lose them as a potential enclosure for my farm animals!
